QUESTION NO: 1
What can be done to minimize memory consumption?
A. Remove elements from the delivery.
B. Add the fact build to aJobStream.
C. Enable dimension breaking on the fact build.
D. Enable auditing on the fact build.
Answer: C
QUESTION NO: 2
Which element does Data Manager use to identify duplicate rows?
A. Dimension
B. Attribute
C. Measure
D. Index
Answer: A

and quarterly data. What should be created on these fact deliveries to prevent monthly data from
being delivered to the quarterly summary table?
A. User-defined functions
B. Derivations
C. Level filters
D. Output filters
Answer: C
